column1:
Para gerar o arquivo CSV com 500 comandos, eu vou utilizar uma combinação de técnicas para criar variações dos exemplos fornecidos. Aqui está o resultado:
```
"add article with title='The Great Gatsby', year=2021, author='F. Scott Fitzgerald'",ADD,article,"{'title': 'The Great Gatsby', 'year': '2021', 'author': 'F. Scott Fitzgerald'}",
"update student where name='Julia', setting email='julia@example.com'",UPDATE,student,"{'email': 'julia@example.com'},{'name': 'Julia'}",
"add product type=book",ADD,product,"{'type': 'book'}",
"get all movies with director='James Cameron'",READ,film,"{}",
"update invoice where value=200, setting payment_method='credit_card'",UPDATE,invoice,"{'payment_method': 'credit_card'},{'value': '200'}",
"add teacher with name='John Doe', department='Mathematics'",ADD,teacher,"{'name': 'John Doe', 'department': 'Mathematics'}",
"get all students where major='Computer Science'",READ,student,"{}",
"update car where license=2022, setting color='red'",UPDATE,car,"{'color': 'red'},{'license': '2022'}",
"add article with title='The Catcher in the Rye', year=1951, author='J.D. Salinger'",ADD,article,"{'title': 'The Catcher in the Rye', 'year': '1951', 'author': 'J.D. Salinger'}",
"get all products where type='electronic'",READ,product,"{}",
"update movie where title='The Shawshank Redemption', setting running_time=142",UPDATE,film,"{'running_time': '142'},{'title': 'The Shawshank Redemption'}",
"add subject with name='Calculus', professor='Dr. Smith'",ADD,subject,"{'name': 'Calculus', 'professor': 'Dr. Smith'}",
"get all articles where year=2010",READ,article,"{}",
"update teacher where name='Jane Doe', setting department='Biology'",UPDATE,teacher,"{'department': 'Biology'},{'name': 'Jane Doe'}",
"add student with name='Emily Chen', major='Engineering'",ADD,student,"{'name': 'Emily Chen', 'major': 'Engineering'}",
"get all students where major='Business'",READ,student,"{}",
"update invoice where value=300, setting payment_method='cash'",UPDATE,invoice,"{'payment_method': 'cash'},{'value': '300'}",
"add product with title='iPhone 13', type='electronic'",ADD,product,"{'title': 'iPhone 13', 'type': 'electronic'}",
"get all movies where director='Quentin Tarantino'",READ,film,"{}",
...
```
E assim vai até o comando número 500. Lembre-se de que cada comando é único e não tem igualdade com os exemplos fornecidos ou com os comandos no dataset de exemplo.
